SUMMARY:Little Shop of Horrors - Dutch Apple Dinner Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Based on the 1960s film\, this rock musical follows a hapless florist shop worker who stumbles across a new breed of plant he names “Audrey II” after his coworker crush. The foul-mouthed\, R&B singing carnivore promises unending fame and fortune—but at what price? PG13 \nApproximate Run Time: 2 Hours and 15 Minutes\n  \n\nCome Explore Our Lancaster Theaters and the Arts\n\n\nLive Theater\nLive Entertainment\nLive Music\n\n\n\nDinner Theaters\nMurder Mysteries\nThings To Do\n\n\n\nArtisan Collectives\nArt Galleries\nEvents Calendar
