SUMMARY:Enchanted at Magic & Wonder
DESCRIPTION:BRAND NEW MAGIC SHOW for 2026! \nWhat begins as a single step into a forgotten magic shop transforms into a spellbinding magical experience for the whole family. Enchanted is an invitation into the extraordinary where every artifact holds a secret and every illusion becomes a doorway to another world. Filled with jaw-dropping effects and immersive storytelling\, this unforgettable journey will transport guests out of reality and into the unimaginable! \n\nCome Explore Our Lancaster Theaters and the Arts\n\n\nLive Theater\nLive Entertainment\nLive Music\n\n\n\nDinner Theaters\nMurder Mysteries\nThings To Do\n\n\n\nArtisan Collectives\nArt Galleries\nEvents Calendar
