SUMMARY:Mark Lowry with Endless Highway and The Sound - American Music Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Mark Lowry is known around the world as a trusted voice in the realm of gospel music and beyond.  He started making music at age 11 and now\, more than five decades later\, his legacy is forever sealed as an innately entertaining communicator who can\, at once\, make audiences laugh\, cry\, and think.  Mark is a singer\, storyteller\, humorist\, author\, and songwriter\, whose lyric to “Mary\, Did You Know?” resulted in one of the most loved modern Christmas songs of this century. \nEndless Highway is a rapidly rising family group with unmatchable harmonies and a stylistically diverse program: combining elements of acoustic and bluegrass music alongside sweeping orchestrations that effortlessly blend to create unforgettable performances. \n\nCome Explore Our Lancaster Theaters and the Arts\n\n\nLive Theater\nLive Entertainment\nLive Music\n\n\n\nDinner Theaters\nMurder Mysteries\nThings To Do\n\n\n\nArtisan Collectives\nArt Galleries\nEvents Calendar
