SUMMARY:Menopause The Musical 2: Cruising Through ‘The Change’® at American Music Theatre
DESCRIPTION:All aboard\, sisters! The hysterical sequel to the smash-hit Menopause The Musical® is finally here! Five years after their chance encounter in a department store\, we set sail with our beloved ladies for more high jinks on the high seas. Menopause The Musical 2: Cruising Through ‘The Change’® is a hilarious and heartfelt look at the joys of menopause and friendship — plus hot flashes\, mood swings\, and memory lapses! Join us on a trip of self-discovery\, backed by a new soundtrack of toe-tapping parodied hits from the 70s\, 80s and 90s. For these four ladies\, menopause was not the end\, but the beginning of a beautiful friendship where love conquers all\, and friendships never fail. \n\nCome Explore Our Lancaster Theaters and the Arts\n\n\nLive Theater\nLive Entertainment\nLive Music\n\n\n\nDinner Theaters\nMurder Mysteries\nThings To Do\n\n\n\nArtisan Collectives\nArt Galleries\nEvents Calendar
