SUMMARY:West Earl Quilt & Consignment Auction
DESCRIPTION:We are once again doing a full in-person Annual Quilt & Consignment Auction on Saturday\, March 15 starting around 8 AM with most of the blocks closing by 3 PM.  All proceeds from this benefit auction help to offset our 100% Volunteer Fire Co. annual operating expenses. \nSeparate food sales will be happening all day. \nConsignments and donations will be accepted up until Friday evening at 9 PM the night before. \n*NOTE* When putting our Address in your GPS you may need to type in the City as West Earl Township \nThe West Earl Quilt Consignment Auction falls on the 3rd Saturday of March every year. \nIf you can’t make it this weekend\, check out our full list of upcoming Mud Sales on LancasterPA.com. \nPlease Note: Many of the Fire Companies holding mud sales can always use extra help on the days they receive items and the day of the event.  It takes a LOT of labor to put on a mud sale. \n* Date Confirmed by West Earl Fire Station
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/west-earl-quilt-consignment-auction/
