SUMMARY:Airville Fire Company Spring Consignment and Quilt Auction
DESCRIPTION:Announcing the 21st Annual Airville Volunteer Fire Company\nQuilt Sale and Consignment Auction\, otherwise known as The Airville”Mud Sale”. \nTo be held on Sat. March 15\,2025 starting at 8:00 AM. \nCome early for your egg sandwiches and donuts. \nSale will be held at the fire house – 3576 Delta Rd Airville PA 17302. \nWe sell everything\, more than 100 quilts\, Longaberger baskets\, crafts\, furniture\, plants\, hay\, straw\, building materials\, farm equipment\, lawn furniture\, sheds\, wagon loads of small household items\, you name it we just might have it!! \n10 or more auctioneers running all day! \nCome early stay all day. \nGreat homemade food. Donuts and pretzels made fresh there all day. Chicken and pork bar b que\, fresh cut French fries\, baked goods\, soup\, subs\, sandwiches\, and many more items too numerous to mention. \nCome join the fun\, you won’t be disappointed!! \nWe are the only Fire Company Mud Sale in York County\, if you’ve never been to one you should come check us out! \nThe Airville Fire Company Spring Consignment and Quilt Auction usually falls on the 3rd Saturday of March every year. \n\nMud Sales are a unique Lancaster County tradition to raise funds for local volunteer fire companies. See our complete schedule of Lancaster County mud sales. \nPlease Note: Many of the Fire Companies holding mud sales can always use extra help on the days they receive items and the day of the event.  It takes a LOT of labor to put on a mud sale. \n \n* 2026 Date Confirmed by Airville Volunteer Fire Company
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/airville-mud-sale/2026-03-21/
LOCATION:Airville Fire Company\, 3576 Delta Road\, Airville\, PA\, 17302\, United States
CATEGORIES:Amish,Fairs & Festivals,Food & Beverage Events,Mud Sales
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancasterpa.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Airville.png
