SUMMARY:Bridges & Brunch with Strasburg Scooter Tours
DESCRIPTION:Experience a relaxing morning ride through the back roads of Amish Country in Lancaster County\, PA. Along the way to a 19th century covered bridge\, enjoy the scenery of rolling hills\, breathtaking views\, and our Amish neighbors going about their daily routines. \nItinerary\nDuration: 1.5-2 hours Some of our past tours have included: \n\nA guided tour of one of Lancaster County’s most beautiful covered bridges\nAn opportunity for a close up of daily life in Amish Country\n$10 dining voucher to one of two of Strasburg’s favorites brunch spots\, Casey Jones’ Restaurant and Speckled Hen* \n\nAnd each trip is unique\, so you never know what we might have in store for you! \n*Unfortunately\, we regret to inform you that some of the food offerings on the tour may not be considered ‘Kosher.’ We apologize for any inconvenience.
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/strasburg-scooter-tours-bridges-brunch/2026-03-30/
LOCATION:Strasburg Scooter Tours\, 246 N Decatur Street\, Strasburg\, 17579\, United States
